data.description: VERY WELL APPOINTED 4TH FLOOR UNIT FACES NORTH FOR AN ALL YEAR SHADY COVERED BALCONY, ACCESSED BY THE GREAT ROOM AND THE SECONDARY BEDROOM. CUSTOM CARPETS AND WINDOW COVERINGS ALL AROUND !  CROWN MOULDINGS AND CHAIR RAILS ADD A VERY CLASSY AND DISTINGUISHED AMBIANCE. BALCONY OVERLOOKS TREE LINED GREENBELT . LAUNDRY IN UTILITY ROOM LOCATED IN THE UNIT. SECURED UNDERGROUND PARKING WITH ELEVATOR TO ALL FLOORS. ONE OF THE LARGEST FLOORPLANS AVAILLABLE IN THE DEVELOPMENT. ENJOY LOTS OF AMENITIES INCLUDING POOL, GYM AND TENNIS COURTS, RV STORAGE JUST 100 YARDS TO THE EAST,VERY CLOSE TO RESTAURANTS AND RETAIL STORES -  THIS COULD BE THE ONE !
